records.addlTxt: The appeal record is hereby returned to the Clerk of Circuit Court for Chippewa County.

It is Ordered that the judgments in 16CF51 and 16CF70 are modified and, as modified, are summarily affirmed; the judgment in 16CF588 is summarily affirmed and the order denying Johnson's postconviction motion for plea withdrawal is summarily affirmed. 
It is further Ordered that Atty Kachinsky is relieved of his obligation to represent defendant in these matters. 
It is further ordered that this summary disposition order will not be published.
